{"tid":2191100,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求mATX靜音機箱推介 (附砌機list求屌醒)(附散熱圖).","createTime":"2020-09-06T08:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T10:17:22.000Z","uid":288304,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"836525c824715da8775b79b5f2e342bc959d8ad6","tid":2191100,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"本身用緊 JONSBO QT01 <br />\n哩隻本身出名靜, 真係好靜, 根箱風扇靜, 又唔震, 夠窄(195mm闊), 如果唔係個前USB柒柒地同想要個Type-C頭, 我真係想清完塵用返佢<br />\n<br />\n想問下依家有咩機箱推介?<br />\n都係要靜為主啦<br />\n唔使燈, 唔使玻璃<br />\n唔要上面入風/有窿(因為有養幾隻貓), 最好USB同On/off果D都唔好在上面<br />\n唔會超頻 (唔超係咪跟U風扇已經好夠? 6年冇砌過機)<br />\n<span class=\"red\">2</span> x 3.5 inch HDD + <span class=\"red\">2</span> x 2.5 inch HDD <br />\n行 7x24 唔會熄機 (長期3-4隻VM行緊, 加埋預12% CPU loading)<br />\n<br />\n機箱Budget : $500-$1200 主要睇下值唔值<br />\n<br />\n來緊想換機, 預計係 i7 + 3070 (唔好屌我用intel, 我有D半公事野要intel先行到)<br />\n<br />\n預10月出機, 如無意外會係哩個組合 (3070會之後先買來加, 用住舊280x先)<br />\n<br />\nASUS 華碩 TUF GAMING B460M-PLUS (WI-FI) B460,DDR-4,LGA 1200,Intel 1GbE,USB3.2 Gen1,WiFi ax mATX M/B  HK$1120  <br />\nG.SKILL DDR4 Aegis Gaming Series F4-3000C16D-32GISB DDR4 3000MHz 32GB Kit (2x16GB)  HK$840  <br />\nANTEC HCG-650 (AN-PS-HCG-650-GOLD) High Current Gamer 650W 80Plus Gold 火牛(Full Modular)  HK$705  <br />\nIntel 8 Cores 16 Threads Core i7-10700 Comet Lake (2.9GHz,16MB Cache,LGA 1200,14nm) CPU BOX 盒裝  HK$2530<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/O6yLeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FO6yLeb.jpg&h=7a82d2a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/luw94K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fluw94K.jpg&h=f2cdd900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5VPYik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5VPYik.jpg&h=1756b7c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0083b2d05ab362504c62215ce9e56c9894322f14","tid":2191100,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike